{"tid":1747593,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"反送中運動中的物理(3)----布袋彈懷疑爆眼事件","createTime":"2019-11-23T09:47:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T09:47:30.000Z","uid":325563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"488cdf541c90cf4f3e97fdff6253d1117c313261","tid":1747593,"uid":325563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:47:30.000Z","msg":"於八月十一月晚上，一名在尖沙咀警署外的女士懷疑被布袋彈所傷，致右眼球破裂。有人指她是被警方發射的布袋彈擊中眼球，但亦有些人指她是被示威者的鋼珠所傷，雙方各執一詞，難以定論。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mNNeCWt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmNNeCWt.jpg&h=9a878753&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QE2qKBx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQE2qKBx.jpg&h=612dc4d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據資料，該名女士戴上的3M 1621眼罩，通過了Z87.1-2003 的安全測試，在測試中這款眼罩正正成功抵受一枚高速撞擊的鋼珠，沒有破裂，因此女事主被鋼珠所傷的機會甚微。且經計算後，一發布袋彈所携帶的動能，比一枚鋼珠的動能大百倍以上，亦有很大機會穿透眼罩，導致女事主爆眼。部分人士所提出&ldquo;布袋彈的威力比鋼珠弱&rdquo;一說，簡直荒天下之大謬。<br />\n下面是分析<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z07x84V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ07x84V.jpg&h=181b8d9f&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aqyA6RC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaqyA6RC.jpg&h=13705c4d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fuiUCYk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfuiUCYk.jpg&h=1c956f4c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZgCNXYn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZgCNXYn.jpg&h=a192ad29&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ozwyTwK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FozwyTwK.jpg&h=8a2bc73d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D3pAnp6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD3pAnp6.jpg&h=f8bba7e4&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/auxNXYt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FauxNXYt.jpg&h=19e77e08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n總結: 純粹的物理計算並不能百分百肯定女士是被警方的布袋彈爆眼，還需在收集人證、物證等證據後才能下結論。諷刺的是，有不少人在得悉充分理據後仍選擇堅持己見。對這種人來說，向他們提供再多的理據也是枉然。<br />\n希望大家可以細心睇下份報告，有咩問題可以提出，我會轉達翻比我個朋友知。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>查警暴，止警謊</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>香港人，加油</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>香港人，反抗</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>香港人，報仇</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港人，返工</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>香港人，投票</strong></span></span></span>"}]}